ria-label=\"References permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/java/library/j-cq03316/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/java/library/j-cq03316/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sonarsource.com/docs/CognitiveComplexity.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.sonarsource.com/docs/CognitiveComplexity.pdf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.sonarqube.org/latest/user-guide/metric-definitions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://docs.sonarqube.org/latest/user-guide/metric-definitions/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.vavr.io/vavr-docs/#_either\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.vavr.io/vavr-docs/#_either</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://fsharpforfunandprofit.com/rop/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://fsharpforfunandprofit.com/rop/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://docs.mipro-proceedings.com/4cows/01_4cows_5333.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://docs.mipro-proceedings.com/4cows/01_4cows_5333.pdf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://adit.io/posts/2013-04-17-functors,_applicatives,_and_monads_in_pictures.html#just-what-is-a-functor,-really\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://adit.io/posts/2013-04-17-functors,_applicatives,_and_monads_in_pictures.html#just-what-is-a-functor,-really</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://codurance.com/2018/08/09/the-functional-sty